title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Apr 7 2022
description:
Clay and Buck challenge Mitt Romney to come on the show and defend his recent votes. Senate votes to confirm KBJ, with three GOP votes. Missouri Attorney General Eric Schmitt joins C&B to talk about suing the Biden Regime for rescinding Title 42. Coming tomorrow: '80s vs. '90s. University of Chicago student slams Brian Stelter with great question about CNN.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
